HEADWORD: Abirritation
<hw>Ab*ir`ri*ta"tion</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A pathological condition opposite to that of
irritation; debility; lack of strength; asthenia.</def>
